broker

Class StockBroker

  • java.lang.Object
    • broker.StockBroker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class StockBroker
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class to Implement Functions of Broker related to stocks. It has an attribute function of type ATM, so all the methods can be calibrated to ATM.date.
